  特殊角色背景故事定义 / Special Character Backstory Definitions
  
  背景故事定义角色的童年和成年经历，影响技能和特质。
  Backstories define childhood and adulthood experiences, affecting skills and traits.
  
  占位符使用说明 / Placeholder Usage:
  - [PAWN_nameDef] - 角色名称 / Character name
  - [PAWN_pronoun] - 代词（他/她）/ Pronoun (he/she)
  - [PAWN_possessive] - 物主代词（他的/她的）/ Possessive (his/her)
  - [PAWN_objective] - 宾格代词（他/她）/ Objective pronoun (him/her)
  
  参考 / Reference:
  - RimWorld Core: Backstories.xml
-->
